<!DOCTYPE <!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title><%= user.name %>e</title>
</head>
<body>

     <!-- include our head from layouts/header -->
     <% include ./layouts/header %>

     <h2 class="user-name"><%= user.name %></h2>
     <!-- <img class="user-pic" src="../public/images/profile-picture.png" alt="user profile image"/> -->
     <img class="user-pic" src="<%= user.img %>" alt="user profile image"/>

     <div class="user-info">
         <h3>User Info</h3>
         <p>
             Mea at adhuc tation salutatus, sed at noluisse phaedrum forensibus. 
             Ad est legere populo expetendis, insolens disputando cu vim, graeco copiosae ne pri.
             Mei quis necessitatibus in, eam dico simul dissentias an, id quo sint velit.
             Ut ius unum simul, nam eius mazim ornatus no, mazim nostro tritani cu sit. 
         </p>
     </div>

     <h3>Friends</h3>
     <!-- check if user has friends -->
     <% if(user.friends){ %>
         <ul>
             <% user.friends.forEach((friend)=>{ %>
                 <li><%= friend %></li>
             <% }) %>
         </ul>
     <% }else{ %>
         <button>Find Friends</button>
     <% } %>

     <!-- script external file -->
     <script src="/script.js"></script>
    
</body>
</html>